Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:15.60,INCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be5}无论是感激还是告别　正因此刻我才能说出口
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------TEXT-----------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.92,0:01:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶  你不游泳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.98,0:01:45.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想被晒伤
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.76,0:01:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听小菜说过了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说你买了一套非常可爱的泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:52.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得都到海边来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.69,0:01:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道只肯给彻先生一个人看吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你个毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在旅行的时候都骂人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.03,0:02:09.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花你们不去游泳吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.11,0:02:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民她不想被晒…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.39,0:02:24.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.52,0:02:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是很浪费哦  鹤来同学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.03,0:02:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难得一次修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.63,0:02:32.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.99,0:02:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花  用擒拿技把鹤来同学擒住
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.25,0:02:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就这样站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.82,0:02:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱～掉～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一～二～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛…毛蛋
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.64,0:03:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名  结名  结名…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.48,0:03:20.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗  还不肯放手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.76,0:03:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我还是没办法对鹤来死心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:25.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好累
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs36\bord1}要学的事的清单：\N　迎接的时候的寒暄语\N　领客人进房间的时候的言行举止\N　摆放饭菜时的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.88,0:03:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摆放饭菜时的动作是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.55,0:03:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答复时的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:38.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.26,0:03:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天还上了一天班
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我第一次上其他旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.69,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要学会好多东西带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢大家～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一个  绪花
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为人家还没听过绪花唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:04:02.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  还没和松前同学一起去过卡拉OK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想听
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:07.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.76,0:04:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鹭慕情冬景色！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.46,0:04:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为啥是演歌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.45,0:04:16.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是上次的客人教会我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花真的好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人感慨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青鹭山哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为何  哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.05,0:04:39.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比喜翠庄还要大…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是当然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要供那么多人住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.97,0:04:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长途跋涉真是辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到福阳旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:54.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  多谢多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:56.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请往这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.13,0:04:59.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请让我来指引各位去房间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:06.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时总是我给别人带路
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.73,0:05:11.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以总有点淡定不下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.84,0:05:15.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们明明是客人的说～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:17.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这指甲是怎么回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.55,0:05:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在说明手册上写得明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手指甲要剪短  也不准染色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.82,0:05:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.65,0:05:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我去把那给洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.46,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有你妆也上得太浓了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.70,0:05:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.16,0:05:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你得说实在是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊  那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这掌柜怪吓人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.30,0:05:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是洋辅君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋辅君  呀嗬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.46,0:05:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名  是结名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.09,0:05:53.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓了我一跳  今天的团体客人原来是结名的学校啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.15,0:05:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋辅君打扮成这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.23,0:05:59.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年开始我就当上掌柜了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.40,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然现在还在见习中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:08.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是继承人～真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.79,0:06:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是哪根葱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢直呼结名大人的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结…结名同学～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.28,0:06:20.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么洋辅君  我们要麻烦你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…刚才那人是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日渡洋辅君  是我的远方亲戚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.46,0:06:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是这个旅馆的继承人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.71,0:06:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更是我的未婚夫～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.04,0:06:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.05,0:06:43.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未婚夫！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.19,0:06:52.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家里是超一流的老字号旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是班里的偶像  身材姣好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连未婚夫都有了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一样是旅馆的外孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.22,0:07:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却一个天上一个地下…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光比旅馆的话你倒还没输
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:09.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说人比人的话我一败涂地是吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.63,0:07:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要向她告白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:20.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都说过自己有未婚夫了  到底在想些什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:29.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是有喜欢的人的话  肯定不该接受告白的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.85,0:07:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为觉得对不起彻先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:33.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又没在说我！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来  我有话想对你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:42.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看那边那边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来同学也要被告白了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.67,0:07:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一等  鹤来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.33,0:07:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我果然喜欢你！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.55,0:08:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次那个人…你已经在跟他交往了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.91,0:08:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还没的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你个毛蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  啥意思  是指OK吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毛蛋是一个略称
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是让人诧异到…咦  什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.04,0:08:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹤来！等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…孤单？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.30,0:08:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.85,0:08:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是青春呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.38,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿孝…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.15,0:08:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四十万的女人  是不会轻言放弃的——
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问他喜欢我哪一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.10,0:09:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后他回答说全部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得这根本不算是个回答吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.71,0:09:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.56,0:09:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情就是这样  于是我就给拒绝掉了～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.62,0:09:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉你应付自如呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.67,0:09:14.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我要是被告白了  脑子里就会一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心里小鹿乱撞…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑子里就只会一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.58,0:09:25.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛人家不是很懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.29,0:09:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过小鹿乱撞这个我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:31.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人告白感觉果然很棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗  你都有未婚夫了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.34,0:09:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.88,0:09:42.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为被人告白很开心呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是洋辅君
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.74,0:09:47.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.54,0:09:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是很懂结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么话嘛好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花的班级头一天就去海边了？好棒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.73,0:10:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜的班级呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.04,0:10:14.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去农场见学和参观遗迹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.34,0:10:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好土
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好土
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.57,0:10:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明好想去游泳的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过明天就能游了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还带来了比赛用泳装
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.87,0:10:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小民你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:27.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她被告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.83,0:10:30.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  你多嘴什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.64,0:10:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你的回复是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别多问
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.76,0:10:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄的各位关系都好好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.56,0:10:43.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么大家  开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.22,0:10:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能排出那么多的餐点还真够壮观呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄看不到这种情景嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.59,0:10:58.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,福屋倒是一直会有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我们这边要来这么多客人可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.75,0:11:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是摆好饭菜就已经要忙到深夜了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半餐具和食材都不够用…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.30,0:11:12.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厨房要忙翻天了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.39,0:11:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就靠四个人来摆好这么多饭菜的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.62,0:11:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作时间中别摆弄手机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.22,0:11:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都给我关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.78,0:11:42.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像又没什么了不起的了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.94,0:11:47.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,味道真棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  接下来就去泡澡泡澡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:04.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也用不着连修学旅行的时候都不放过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  总觉得很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:08.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.81,0:12:10.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就好像自由式游泳的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是会在左边换气一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:17.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晒伤的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.03,0:12:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.18,0:12:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘记带化妆水了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.32,0:12:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有带着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澡堂不知道是什么样子的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.59,0:12:26.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然应该是很宽敞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.00,0:12:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是还是以前来时那样没变过的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.71,0:12:34.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  结名同学已经是未婚妻了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家旅馆的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.89,0:12:37.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是旅馆的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.62,0:12:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好啊  结名同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.23,0:12:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我也从小时候就努力学习的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.80,0:12:45.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不定现在就是一个出色的女服务员了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.60,0:12:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔  绪花想做女服务员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.68,0:12:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦…说起来我真是想当女服务员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:59.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什么  莫名其妙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.57,0:13:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太明白…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我也想雪愿变得能出色完成旅馆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.08,0:13:08.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有这样的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.98,0:13:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  雪愿…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.83,0:13:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前也有说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.95,0:13:19.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向着目标努力的决心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.74,0:13:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带来的各种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.87,0:13:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就雪愿能成为绪花的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们还不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪成为更好的朋友愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}成为愿  更好的朋友雪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.32,0:13:40.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用法越来越奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.31,0:13:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我卸货
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.81,0:13:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗碗处等着盘子洗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.01,0:13:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是慢吞吞的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.06,0:13:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的  在看什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是凶呢  洋辅君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  原来是结名
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.80,0:14:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋辅君  这边是绪花和鹤来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.48,0:14:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在喜翠庄工作的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.99,0:14:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.65,0:14:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜翠庄
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汤乃鹭的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.43,0:14:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没听过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以参观一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  可以呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.70,0:14:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这样端到客人面前吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们家的一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.49,0:14:38.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年开始为了削减人力购入的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.24,0:14:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠它真是轻松多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:44.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多少份都能轻松运送
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.70,0:14:47.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女服务员也只要找短期的打工者就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.81,0:14:51.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真了不起呢  已经在考虑经营的事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.85,0:14:52.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.94,0:14:56.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  结名现在有时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.95,0:14:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.42,0:14:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那就去外面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.69,0:15:03.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  剩下的就交给你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.30,0:15:04.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.61,0:15:07.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家对不起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.20,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚正好月亮也漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.55,0:15:13.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀  真是期待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.73,0:15:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个掌柜的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.66,0:15:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过这儿轮不到我们多说话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.35,0:15:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.20,0:15:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:46.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡澡…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.91,0:15:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得就在这附近…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.36,0:16:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:06.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:10.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.56,0:16:11.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小菜…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.83,0:16:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.96,0:16:16.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我还以为是河童…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久没看过晚上的大海了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前还经常在这里玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.32,0:16:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还带着烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.41,0:16:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还学了这边的方言呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,kikkuiyanse来着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:32.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（注：きっくいやんせ  宫崎方言）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.23,0:16:34.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对对  欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nankurunaisa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs36}（注：なんとかなるよ  总会有办法的）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是冲绳话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是来游泳的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.35,0:16:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事小菜一个人就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:45.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.74,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的变可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.85,0:16:49.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洋辅君样子也很适合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身掌柜的打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:53.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还差远着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了让咱家成为日本第一的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.30,0:16:57.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还得更加得努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.06,0:16:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是远大的梦想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.57,0:17:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  没有你的帮助怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.39,0:17:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成为小洋的妻子当一个日本第一的老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.60,0:17:12.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是有这样的约定吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候的约定总是很纯真呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.47,0:17:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为想着约定一定会实现的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:23.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是认真要去实现的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.33,0:17:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括让咱家的旅馆成为日本第一的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.38,0:17:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…结名
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.00,0:17:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕业了就来我这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.37,0:17:38.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来把这里变成比福屋更厉害的旅馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.70,0:17:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当社长  你当老板娘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:43.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.03,0:17:50.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当老板娘…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来管理旅馆的工作…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.79,0:17:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐  洋辅君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢旅馆的工作吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.13,0:18:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  突然问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:01.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.99,0:18:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问起喜欢还是讨厌的话  当然喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.91,0:18:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  该去泡澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.79,0:18:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那明天见了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:16.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  答复呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.84,0:18:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保留～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.78,0:18:29.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是老样子莫名其妙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢旅馆的工作吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.89,0:19:06.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有话要说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:08.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经都打扫完了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.74,0:19:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没  但有话想要先说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.20,0:19:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去先完成再说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.82,0:19:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是和你说过工作的安排都是订好的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我好好按照说明手册上的做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天该我负责晒被子…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.01,0:19:37.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,修学旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.02,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白闹钟了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么等到早餐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续睡呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都醒了已经
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.73,0:19:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两个已经醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:20:00.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不好意思  吵醒你了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.71,0:20:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆的早晨真是早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.09,0:20:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.84,0:20:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去和河童…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.43,0:20:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.88,0:20:17.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绪花真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.54,0:20:25.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.14,0:20:28.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.87,0:20:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么怎么那么的  已经决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.32,0:20:34.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  洋辅君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工的人突然说想要辞职
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.57,0:20:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然辞职这边很困扰的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上想去和掌柜的说的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他不听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.15,0:20:56.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌柜的把工作推给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己去和女朋友…是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.06,0:21:03.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是该说是干不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.37,0:21:05.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有干下去的意思来着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且说白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.33,0:21:09.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份工作又累还一点都不合算
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.69,0:21:11.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.26,0:21:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话  掌柜的态度也让人不爽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.60,0:21:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙  真是瞎编乱造
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.22,0:21:14.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…掌柜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.91,0:21:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在旅馆工作可是很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没兴趣的人是坚持不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕给再多的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.39,0:21:29.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做的事是坚持不下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.86,0:21:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不是喜欢的事就不能雪愿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.72,0:21:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.09,0:21:40.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把其中最想做的事当成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.78,0:21:42.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我想做的事里并没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.94,0:21:48.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旅馆的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是昨天的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.54,0:22:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结名同学…
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.88,0:23:34.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我就是没工作过
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.88,0:23:35.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}你才是不可理喻！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}诶  那样想的只有绪花呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:40.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土…土特产呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.28,0:23:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是指这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
